Package com.serena.dmclient.collections Description

This package provides the collection interfaces that represent groups of Dimensions objects. The abstract root collection is DimensionsObjectCollection. This interface specifies the common operations supported by all collections, such as iterating through the collection objects, getting a Dimensions object by its name, removing a Dimensions object, and refreshing the collection to reflect most recent changes to the underlying database schema.

The derived collection interfaces such as FileFormats and Products usually define additional type-safe operations.
